Name: Midnight Calling: Anabel Collector's Edition
About the game: The castle is calling! Play as the lovely Anabel, whose father, Henry, disappeared several years ago. Now he’s calling to you in your dreams and needs your help. Travel back to your hometown to save your father and uncover the secrets of Midnight Castle! A batty sidekick, a variety of hidden-object puzzles, morphing objects, Rube Goldberg-style super puzzles, and tons of collectibles make this a not-to-be-missed adventure! Fans of the blockbuster game Midnight Castle will thrill to this Elephant Games’ prequel! Save Midnight Castle from a new danger in the bonus game! Replay your favorite hidden-object puzzles and mini-games! Enjoy exclusive wallpapers, concept art, and the soundtrack! Uncover all the secrets with the available Strategy Guide!
